attachments.title: May SF Slack Developers' Meetup
attachments.text: Come learn about how to build great products on the Slack Platform! Overcoming the technical hurdles to building and deploying Slack Apps is only half the battle—the other half is coming to terms with conversational UX, and understand what a great product looks like when built on top of chat. Hear insightful commentary and learn best practices for building your product. We're still getting our speaker list together, but watch this space! Confirmed speakers: Sonya Mann, exolymph.news: "Boundaries for Bots"Paolo Perazzo, Kyber: TBDTony Lucas, Converse: "Commands vs Conversations"Sean Stephenson, Pixar: "Bot Lightyear"
